Test Case 3:Order detail page (Purchase Now)

Test Case Title: Order detail page (Purchase Now)
Test Case ID: Order detail page (Purchase Now) FT-03

Description: Verify that users can add to cart and purchase

Preconditions:
The seller has posted the products in his store and shared his store link
the store link in opened on a browser
User is on the product page
User clicked Purchase now

Test Steps:
Verify that you can see the order details
clink increment to increase product quantity and decrease
Click add delivery info to add delivery details
    Add name 
    Phone number
    Email address
    Delivery address and landmark
Choose delivery options 
Accept terms and condition

Expected Results:
The user should be able to increment product quantity, add delivery details and delivery options and accept terms and condition and make payment 
Actual Result: 
The user is able to increment product quantity, add delivery details and delivery options and accept terms and condition and make payment
